{
  "chapter": 35,
  "chapter_summary": "第三十五回\"一决胜负\"中，叶开与上官小仙在冷香园对峙。上官小仙坦承自己既是金钱帮帮主又是魔教教主，并以丁灵琳的性命要挟叶开。此时丁灵琳从床下地窖中现身，揭露她早已杀死韩贞并藏身其下，反将了上官小仙一军。上官小仙亮出金刚不坏大搜神手套和上天入地大搜魂针两大绝学，与叶开的飞刀形成对决之势。丁灵琳被迫退出门外等待。最终叶开以小李飞刀获胜，但并未杀死上官小仙，体现了\"宽恕远比报复更伟大\"的飞刀精神——爱而非恨才是小李飞刀的力量之源。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我来的时候，还不想揭穿这件事的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 6,
      "line_end": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "因为……",
      "tone": "犹豫",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "是不是因为你还有点不忍？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你非但不忍，也不敢。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "不敢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为你根本连一点证据都没有，只凭推测，是不能定人罪的。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 22,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可是丁灵琳出了事，你就立刻不顾一切了。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 28,
      "line_end": 28
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "她到处闯祸生事，到处惹麻烦，还几乎一刀把你杀死，你不在的时候，她连半天都等不得，就急着要嫁人，嫁一次还不够，一夜间她就嫁给了两个男人，像这么样一个女人，有哪点值得你为她如此牺牲？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我也想不通。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 40,
      "line_end": 40
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那么你……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我只知道，就算她再杀我十次，再嫁给十个男人，我还是一样会这么样对她的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "因为我知道她对我是真心的，我信任她。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 50
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "现在你还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "没有了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "但我却还有一点不能不说。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我的确连一点证据都没有，这些事你本不必承认的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我也不必否认。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 72,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "因为我不但是金钱帮的帮主，还是魔教的教主，我不但掌握了天下最可怕的两大帮派，还掌握了丁灵琳的性命，我无论是承认也好，是否认也好，你都只有听着。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "现在你还有什么话说？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 84,
      "line_end": 84
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "丁灵琳现在还活着，你想不想要她活下去？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 88,
      "line_end": 88
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "想。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "那么我说的话，你就要听着，每个字都仔细听着。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "她说的话，你连一个字都不必听，因为，她根本就是在放屁。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你会的事，我都会。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你会骗人，我也会，你会杀人，我也会，而且绝不比你差。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你要韩贞来杀我，再想法子让小叶以为我是发疯而死的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你一定想不到我反而杀了他。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你会在我的炖鸡面里下迷药，我也会在他喝的茶里下迷药。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "他当然不会提防一个已发了疯的女人，就好像我们以前没确提防你一样。这法子本是我从你那里学来的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我把他的尸体送到床下去的时候，才发现床下面有个地窖，是藏酒的地方。原来冷香园的酒都是藏在这种地窖里的，所以那天我们在外面连一瓶酒都找不到。我知道你们一定会来，所以我就藏入地窖里，却将尸体摆在外面。我算准你看到韩贞死了后，一定会大吃一惊，绝不会再注意到下面还有个地窖。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我还想听听你们在上面说些什么，看他是不是会被你骗走。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 162,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "其实我也知道你这次绝不会再上她当的，你果然没有让我失望。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这就是传说中的金刚不坏，大搜神手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这手本是准备用来对付吕迪和郭定的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我看得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "可惜他们却让我失望了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "这是我的上天入地，大搜魂针。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "杨天他们四个人，就是死在我这种针下的。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我也看得出。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "昔年梅花盗的梅花针，已令天下武林中人丧胆。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我听说过。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "但是我可以保证，我这种针远比梅花针更可怕。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "你这种针想必是准备用来对付我的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你的刀呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "刀在。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我也知道你的刀是无所不在，无所不至的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 234
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你的刀无所不在，无所不至，我的针也一样。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你也永远无法想像，我的针会从什么地方发出来，更无法想像它是怎么发出来的。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我不会去想，也不必想。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 262
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "你若认为你能封住我的出手，你就错了。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "我的针如恒河沙数，你的刀却有限。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我的刀只要一柄就已足够。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "也许这就是命运。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 272,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "命运？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "也许我命中注定，迟早总要和你一决胜负的。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "正如昔年的上官帮主，是命中注定了要和小李探花一决胜负一样。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "昔年的上官帮主，的确不愧为一世之雄，只可惜现在……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "昔年的上官帮主虽已不在，今日的上官帮主却还在。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "飞刀也在。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ye_kai",
      "text": "昔年他们那一战，虽足以惊天地，泣鬼神，却没有人能亲眼看到。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "今日你们这一战，却一定会有人亲眼看到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 296,
      "line_end": 296
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "没有。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "有。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 300,
      "line_end": 300
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "你想看？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "text": "我一定能看得到。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 304,
      "line_end": 304
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "那么你就只有看着叶开死。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_guan_xiao_xian",
      "speaker_name": "上官小仙",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "你若在这里，我的飞针出手，第一个要对付的就是你，他若为你分心他就只有死。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "speaker_name": "丁灵琳",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "上官小仙呢？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 382,
      "line_end": 382
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ye_kai",
      "speaker_name": "叶开",
      "listener": "char_ding_ling_lin",
      "text": "她败了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 35,
      "line_start": 386,
      "line_end": 386
    }
  ],
